{"tid":454444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔「脫北者」親述遭黑衣女勒頸壓鎖骨","createTime":"2017-11-01T06:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T04:57:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"26d6db847ee9dbe78c0dc9d9c63eeffbfba032cd","tid":454444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171101/large/1509507139_84c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171101%2Flarge%2F1509507139_84c4.jpg&h=66644965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔太湖花園姓金(48歲)的女住客，昨晚聲稱在大廈後樓梯遭箍頸( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2hr2QNZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2hr2QNZ&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e6f745d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2hr2QNZ</a> )，經急症室醫生診治後，已經回家休養，只是頸項仍留有兩條紅痕。她接受訪問時，向記者道出一段段不為人所知的經歷。她自稱是脫北者，自2014年一宗官司令身份曝光後，今次已經是第二次在住所後樓梯遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n金女指出，由於自己身份特殊，已第4次改名換姓。惟上次官司令其身份曝光後，麻煩事接踵而來。<br />\n<br />\n金女續稱，去年12月一個晚上，她返回住所時，遭一名操平壤口音的女子持刀恐嚇，一度欲推其入屋，其後被推往後樓梯及碌落樓梯，勒令她收聲。事隔差不多一年，昨晚她在住所外走廊，又遭一名全身穿黑衣、戴黑色帽及口罩的女子，從後以膠帶勒頸，並用力按壓其鎖骨，再以毛巾纏著拖到後樓梯，並以山東口音喝罵她：「你不要再說啦！」由7樓拖落5樓。她奮力掙扎，踢倒垃圾筒，最終對方逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n對於兩度遇襲，金女似乎見慣不怪，但如租約期滿，打算遷出「避難」。金女自稱有驚恐症，需服食藥物，對答時亦較為遲緩，她慶幸有丈夫在旁默默支持。金女亦指，第一次遇襲後，曾有南韓領事館人員接觸她，而最近她亦曾與居港的「脫北者」聯絡，不排除今次遇襲與此有關。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，2014年，當時姓劉的她，曾在一公司任經理，因患有第三期骨髓癌，不堪支付龐大醫療費，用假單據騙取公司7萬元公幹津貼，被判入獄半年但緩刑兩年，另罰款1.6萬元( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gPJZf0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gPJZf0&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a3de25e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gPJZf0</a> )。當時她自稱年幼時，與胞姊由北韓逃往中國，再被香港一家庭收養，其後獲悉其16名被送往政治勞改營的家人，只得一人生還。<br />\n<br />\n探員今晨返回現場調查，經翻看閉路電視錄影片段，暫未發現有可疑人曾出入大廈。"},{"pid":"a8a36bb0a918be55cf827e950e59417ec190ef5f","tid":454444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171101/57402541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57402541&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6cfdb903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57402541&h=c76847cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171101/57402541</a>"},{"pid":"f82112a615ab949160e7a48f92505be98abb3dc8","tid":454444,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"金仔咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8f1196f0775a04f88efd69a60a9f0f89911f96","tid":454444,"uid":4525,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"北韓都幾無聊"},{"pid":"599e612c87ee311b51ab1251dedf088a2621cdc6","tid":454444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fa14d7da9db1908f5ddce20bd6030ec95fe251","tid":454444,"uid":100150,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"女特務快點來搞我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67717b58a265aa0bc23f44bd4ad1814bb5b21f95","tid":454444,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d128cac243233e8577760934ec50a27d0345cc9","tid":454444,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61e242be21ece72b2b893e81f15cba8a6903a0","tid":454444,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"