,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"金仔搞到黎大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6562ad0a9b9f06945cd800d685224d654acace","tid":454444,"uid":49588,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都幾怪.<br />\n如果事主係北韓人. 佢點分到係山東口音?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你去廣州，佛山，他們一樣是講東話，但你會聽到有明顯嘅分別！<br />\n<br />\n一樣，山東跟北韓隔不太遠，只要長期居住過，喺會聽得出口音的分別！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一種語言，唔同村都會有唔同嘅口音！<br />\n（在中國大陸，村與村之間是30公里至50公里左右）"},{"pid":"6dded6582d1784b2757f3321e110b840a6a3bde5","tid":454444,"uid":59961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}